description: The iShares iBonds Dec 2025 Term Muni Bond ETF seeks to track the investment results of an index composed of investment-grade U.S. municipal bonds maturing after December 31, 2024 and before December 2, 2025.This Fund is covered by U.S. Patent Nos. 8,438,100 and 8,655,770.
name: iShares iBonds Dec 2025 Term Muni Bond ETF
